reviewText:
Now, this is really cool if you like collecting Super Junior's Concerts.
Though if I were to see the one where they were in Korea first, I
wouldn't have purchased this one. The official one where their in
Seoul is the best quality and more official :D

Just got this dvd and i Love it. Wish I could go to one of their concerts! This is the next best thing and i can watch it over and over and over
again! The vendor sent it in time and fast and in good condition. Super Junior Rocks!
